	<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Just like that, you have created a page for your Independence Day website. Isnt that amazing? Now all thats left to do is add your own content, and customize the template to suit your personal style.</span></p><h3><b>Step 2: Customize Your 4th of July Website</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Customizing your 4th of July template is very easy to do and can be done in less than 5 minutes. Just click on any section that you want to customize and use the </span><b>Elementor Editor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> on your left to style your website. Play around with the background colors, typography, and images until you have your own unique WordPress Independence Day website</span></p><p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-489467 aligncenter\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/C2X2Gwvgt1.gif\" alt=\"4th of July\" width=\"1920\" height=\"903\" /></p><h3><b>Step 3: Save Your Independence Day Website Design On MyCloud</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Templately comes with a very useful feature that lets you</span> <a href=\"https://docs.templately.com/home/save-templates-design-on-mycloud/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>save your design on MyCloud</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. With this option, you will be able to reuse your Independence Day website design later on, at any time from anywhere. All you have to do is right-click anywhere on your page and choose the option </span><b>Save Page in Templately</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-34128db elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"34128db\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c88ab91 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"c88ab91\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-edff402 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"edff402\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1600\" height=\"779\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"4th of July\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190.png 1600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-768x374.png 768w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-1536x748.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b26ee87 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b26ee87\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43be22c elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id