(306, 1, '2020-07-18 12:08:45', '2020-07-18 11:08:45', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Fonate</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nActions Mboka is a work of a former student in USA Jacques Ngbondu and his lovely wife Carine Ngbondu. Created in June 2020 by the couple, the association is a result of a long observation of the precariousness social situation and the lack of local development strategies in Mongala province, Kinshasa and the country in general. Threfore, to partcipate in the development event in order to growing the local community, the couple Jacques Ngbondu, decede to create Actions Mboka to contribute to local development by helping the local associations to improve their living social conditions. With a national vision, Actions Mboka works to reduce poverty, mentalities change of he local population and promote the local development of Mongala province.\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<h2>OUR Objectives</h2>\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Train young people in entrepreneurship</li><li>Train young people for responsible leadership in the management of public and community task</li><li>Create a network for local development action</li><li>Involve young leaders in training, debates and conferences at local, national and international levels</li><li>Raising awareness of the Congolese population to take care of themselves through self-determination</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Our values</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Development</li><li>Work </li><li>Leadership</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-18 12:08:45', '2020-07-18 11:08:45', '', 15, 'http://localhost/Action_Mboka/actionmboka/2020/07/18/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
